|GKB-- Reincarnate ----------------------------------------------|000

Very powerful druids sometimes draw deeply from the Marken current to pierce the
veil of death and draw on Gaea's power to create
a new living body for themselves.  By returning
from death in this manner, a druid can avoid much
of the physical and mental damage associated with
death.

